whether we have a recession or not it's&nbsp;
totally possible that your life is getting&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:49.840
worse whilst we are technically not in recession&nbsp;
I think the best example of that is in the 2008&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:58.400
crisis the recession officially ended in the&nbsp;middle 
of 2009 and yet the the 10-15 years since&nbsp;2009

00:01:58.400 --> 00:02:03.480
have seen some of the biggest and fastest&nbsp;
falls in living standards for ordinary people&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:10.960
in the history of the country in peacetime um&nbsp;
you know in the 10 years after 2010 especially&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:17.000
after the election of the the conservative&nbsp;
coalition austerity government we saw 

